f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f6ee8394ddd6789c3c151994def8c05cf45ad6","tid":261920,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二隻既出現係因為以前既人怕開check(類似咁既野)時d人會改數字<br />\n例如 一萬變三萬<br />\n所以特登整新字等人地無得改</blockquote><br />\n有心改 點都改到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你個解釋聽過用喺<br />\n送獎品乙份  唔寫一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咪三種寫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你，我細個成日以為乙份係2份咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 古代果陣啲銀票上面已經用緊柒代7，以防改，所以每隻字結構都會複雜好多<br />\n而乙份我覺得應該係即方便又唔怕比人改既寫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ee97cc0c4e1784edf6536ed177491dd8a4aa86","tid":261920,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二隻既出現係因為以前既人怕開check(類似咁既野)時d人會改數字<br />\n例如 一萬變三萬<br />\n所以特登整新字等人地無得改</blockquote><br />\ncheck？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09668a842fb3bc002af24d4f2ca7ea1114c6724f","tid":261920,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n<br />\n之前在Youtube睇開班鬼佬講數字<br />\n例如法國人個數字系統好痴線，完全反人類。<br />\n<br />\n之後班鬼佬訪問一個支國留學英國既學者<br />\n叫佢介紹中文數字<br />\n<br />\n本來呢樣野好多野好講，<br />\n例如中文行十進制，讀出一個數字有完美邏輯<br />\n一定程度上解釋到華人數學成績較好的原因<br />\n<br />\n點知條仆街有呢d唔講，<br />\non9 9講中國傳統(Traditional Chinese)既1234要寫成壹貳參肆。<br />\n又唔講因咩理由(票據防偽)<br />\n仆佢個街真係震驚拾參億人。"},{"pid":"3c7eef1bd83936b2d2cc88ec61563cdd6b779043","tid":261920,"uid":10890,"like":0